                            <comment id="14476889" author="melix" created="Thu, 18 Dec 2014 14:35:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is fixed but with the same limitation as in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-7191&quot; title=&quot;CompileStatic Will Not Allow Instance Method In Trait To Call Static Method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-7191&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-7191&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, that is to say that it is not possible to call another static method in the trait if the trait is statically compiled.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
